"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-tennis-andy-murray-olympics-retire-paris-gold-medal-b2503921.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The 36-year-old has been speaking openly about his retirement from tennis  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Andy Murrayhas revealed he wants to play at another Olympic Games before he retires.\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 36-year-old hinted on Monday that he isentering the \\\"last few months\\\" of his career.\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 595, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray is the only men's player to win two Olympic singles gold medals, following success in London in 2012 and Rio in 2016, and he wants to play in Paris this summer.\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 597, \"end\": 603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.877263803321588e-29, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 690, \"end\": 696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9987924296869738, \"rank\": 0.001207815461833582, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 709, \"end\": 712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999973319039905, \"rank\": 2.6681031361919595e-06, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 746, \"end\": 751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998647999837, \"rank\": 1.3520009522933146e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Hopefully I can get the chance to compete at another one,\\\" Murray told theToday Programme.\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 826, \"end\": 832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.877263803321588e-29, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray has dropped several clues about the impending end of his career this season, including at the Australian Open at the start of the year.\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 859, \"end\": 865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.877263803321588e-29, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray said after his first-round defeat to Tomas Martin Etcheverry that he may have played his final match at the tournament and may not be back next year.\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1003, \"end\": 1009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.877263803321588e-29, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\