y for [Roger] Federer might not be the right way for [Rafael] Nadal, might not be the right way for [Novak] Djokovic.\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1799, \"end\": 1807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999875310551, \"rank\": 1.2468977582190208e-08, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray claimed a morale-boosting win over Denis Shapovalov in Dubai in MOnday and now takes on Frenchman Ugo Humbert in the second round.\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1810, \"end\": 1816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.877263803321588e-29, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1852, \"end\": 1857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denis_Thatcher\", \"score\": 0.9690027164988377, \"rank\": 0.031071674705805054, \"text\": \"Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denis_Thatcher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denis_Thatcher\"}, {\"begin\": 1872, \"end\": 1877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dubai_Tennis_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999872790005742, \"rank\": 1.0029820044831324e-05, \"text\": \"Dubai\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dubai_Tennis_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dubai_Tennis_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 1915, \"end\": 1926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ugo_Humbert\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ugo Humbert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q21